fields.name: Maintenance Facility
fields.description: The maintenance shop handles routine services such as oil changes, fluid replacements, and safety inspections.

fields.name: Tire Facility
fields.description: The tire shop stocks a wide selection of brands and performs tire fitting, balancing, and rotations.

fields.name: Diagnostic Facility
fields.description: Our diagnostic facility features advanced scanning tools to quickly identify and troubleshoot engine and electrical issues.

fields.name: Alignment Facility
fields.description: The alignment facility uses laser-guided equipment to ensure precise wheel alignment for improved handling and tire longevity.

fields.name: Office
fields.description: The office serves as the central hub for customer service, scheduling, and administrative coordination.

fields.name: Tuning Facility
fields.description: Our tuning facility is equipped with precision tools and software to optimize vehicle performance and engine responsiveness.

fields.name: Carwash Facility
fields.description: The car wash area offers a full exterior and interior detailing service to leave your vehicle spotless.

fields.name: Paint Facility
fields.description: The paint shop includes a dust-free spray booth and color-matching technology for flawless refinishing work.

fields.name: Auto Service
fields.description: Your trusted auto service partner.

fields.name: Throttle Response Tuning
fields.description: Adjusts electronic throttle settings to deliver sharper or smoother pedal response.

fields.name: Scratch and Chip Repair
fields.description: Fills and repaints minor surface scratches and paint chips to restore finish.

fields.name: Tire Rotation Service
fields.description: Rotates tires between positions to even out wear and extend tire life.

fields.name: Full Vehicle Repaint
fields.description: Strips and resprays the entire vehicle with fresh, high-quality automotive paint.

fields.name: Check Engine Light Inspection
fields.description: Investigates reasons behind the check engine light and recommends corrective action.

fields.name: Interior Detailing
fields.description: Vacuuming, stain removal, and surface cleaning to refresh the interior cabin.

fields.name: Wiper Blade Replacement
fields.description: Installs new wiper blades to improve visibility during rain and snow conditions.

fields.name: Suspension System Check
fields.description: Examines shocks, struts, and other suspension parts for issues affecting alignment and stability.

fields.name: Sensor Function Test
fields.description: Verifies operation of oxygen sensors, mass airflow sensors, and other critical components.

fields.name: Four-Wheel Alignment
fields.description: Aligns all four wheels to factory specifications to ensure even tire wear and proper handling.

fields.name: Warranty Verification
fields.description: Confirms manufacturer or shop warranty coverage for eligible parts and services.

fields.name: Service History Lookup
fields.description: Retrieves and reviews a customer's vehicle service history to inform future repairs or maintenance.

fields.name: Tire Installation
fields.description: Installs new tires onto wheels and ensures proper inflation and torque specs.

fields.name: Tire Puncture Repair
fields.description: Seals small punctures or holes in the tire tread caused by road debris.

fields.name: Customer Support Handling
fields.description: Assists customers with inquiries about service options, shop policies, and repair status updates.

fields.name: OBD-II Fault Scan
fields.description: Scans the onboard diagnostic system to retrieve and interpret fault codes for various systems.

fields.name: Battery Replacement
fields.description: Tests and replaces weak or dead vehicle batteries to restore electrical reliability.

fields.name: Steering System Inspection
fields.description: Inspects steering components for play or damage that may affect alignment accuracy.

fields.name: Tire Wear Pattern Analysis
fields.description: Analyzes tire wear patterns to diagnose alignment and suspension issues.

fields.name: Paintless Dent Removal
fields.description: Removes minor dents and dings without the need for sanding or repainting.

fields.name: Turbocharger Tuning
fields.description: Fine-tunes turbo systems to increase power output while maintaining safe operating limits.

fields.name: Oil and Filter Change
fields.description: Replaces engine oil and filters to keep the engine clean and running smoothly.

fields.name: Wax and Polish Service
fields.description: Applies wax and polish to add shine and create a protective barrier on the paint.

fields.name: Toe-In/Toe-Out Correction
fields.description: Fine-tunes the toe settings to correct tracking and ensure smooth driving.

fields.name: Cooling System Diagnosis
fields.description: Assesses radiator, thermostat, and water pump performance to detect overheating causes.

fields.name: Seasonal Tire Changeover
fields.description: Swaps summer and winter tires to match driving conditions for the season.

fields.name: Camber and Caster Adjustment
fields.description: Adjusts camber and caster angles to correct vehicle drift or uneven tire wear.

fields.name: Appointment Scheduling
fields.description: Organizes and manages service appointments based on technician availability and customer preferences.

fields.name: Headlight Restoration
fields.description: Polishes cloudy headlights to restore clarity and improve nighttime visibility.

fields.name: Fuel System Optimization
fields.description: Calibrates the fuel delivery system for improved combustion and engine efficiency.

fields.name: Clear Coat Restoration
fields.description: Polishes and seals the clear coat to enhance gloss and protect against UV damage.

fields.name: Wheel Balancing
fields.description: Balances tires to eliminate vibrations and promote even tread wear.

fields.name: Billing and Invoicing
fields.description: Generates detailed invoices and processes payments for services rendered.

fields.name: Electrical System Diagnosis
fields.description: Checks alternator, battery, and wiring for issues that cause electrical faults or intermittent problems.

fields.name: Belt and Hose Check
fields.description: Inspects drive belts and radiator hoses for signs of cracking, wear, or leaks.

fields.name: Exterior Hand Wash
fields.description: Cleans the exterior using soft mitts, pH-balanced soap, and a spotless rinse.

fields.name: Cold Air Intake Installation
fields.description: Replaces the stock air intake system with a high-performance cold air intake to improve airflow.

fields.name: Work Order Processing
fields.description: Creates and updates internal work orders to track technician tasks and service completion status.

fields.name: Panel Repainting
fields.description: Repaints individual body panels using color-matched paint and clear coat.

fields.name: Engine Performance Analysis
fields.description: Uses sensors and scan data to analyze misfires, fuel trims, and engine response.

fields.name: Dyno Performance Testing
fields.description: Tests the vehicle's power and torque output under load conditions using a dynamometer.

fields.name: Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS) Check
fields.description: Inspects and resets TPMS sensors for proper function and dashboard alert accuracy.

fields.name: ECU Remapping
fields.description: Reprograms the engine control unit to enhance vehicle performance, fuel efficiency, and throttle response.

fields.name: Engine Bay Cleaning
fields.description: Degreases and washes the engine compartment for a clean, professional finish.

fields.name: Multi-Point Vehicle Inspection
fields.description: Performs a comprehensive check of critical vehicle systems and components for wear or damage.

fields.name: Bumper Respray
fields.description: Repairs and repaints front or rear bumpers that have scuffs, chips, or scratches.

fields.name: Fluid Top-Up Service
fields.description: Checks and refills essential fluids such as brake, coolant, windshield, and power steering fluids.

fields.name: Undercarriage Wash
fields.description: Rinses salt and grime from the vehicle's undercarriage to prevent rust and corrosion.
